{"tid":2298722,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone突然間no service，俾apple support玩左兩日都搞唔掂，求救","createTime":"2020-11-24T08:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T15:40:19.000Z","uid":33222,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"70829f8ce24fe3716f8f75daca0b4c9c8b662893","tid":2298722,"uid":33222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:52:48.000Z","msg":"電話係垃圾XR，事源我前日夜晚update左ios14.2<br />\n點知琴日早晨，翻翻下工見到台面部電話突然自己熄機開機，再打開就話&ldquo;流動數據更新失敗&rdquo;姐係無得打出打入，無得用data，官方網站教學就話ios有問題，要重裝就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我打俾apple support，熄機開機轉sim卡重設網絡設定重設所有設定都唔得，個職員實牙實齒話係軟件問題，要我翻去用電腦重新裝過次ios 14.2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁好啦，翻去裝，裝唔到，今日再打電話俾apple support，佢話要我將macbook update到最新嘅mac OS Big Sur，然後就可以裝ios 14.2.1啦！<br />\n如是者我又搞左幾個鐘，都係唔得，都係顯示我已經裝左最新嘅ios，無得再裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有再打俾佢地，今次另一條友話，你裝唔到14.2.1架，你都唔係iPhone 12，我檢測左啦，你係硬件問題，去genius bar比錢整啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我心諗，屌，三次電話個個講嘅野都唔同，退一萬步，就算我真係硬件有問題，按照網站講嘅我都可以重新裝多次ios 14.2姐，最多係裝完都唔work，但唔會連裝都無得裝呀嘛....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以，唔通真係要硬食呢舊錢揾genius？有無自救方法&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5093f1fe326a99bff7f5da81b43c9263c1c013b4","tid":2298722,"uid":73100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:54:11.000Z","msg":"我都係咁 上左ios14 收唔到data 肯定左唔係張卡問題"},{"pid":"e10b79ac92c170ca8e83762e1a6b2e743550e5be","tid":2298722,"uid":341649,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"